c: 18
v: 77
t: "Barasubira kubandanya urugndo rwabo kugeza aho bashikira abantu b’ico gisagara, baca babasaba ibifungurwa baranka kubazimana, baca basanga uruhome rw’inzu yabo rugomba guhenuka, nawe aca ararusanura, intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) aca avuga ati:- iyo ubishaka wari kubasaba agashiruka bute"